001package doctorwhoapp.backend.domain;
002
003public class Doctor extends Person {
004    private int incarnationNumber;
005    private String incarnationName;
006    private String slogan;
007    private Doctor predecessor;
008    private Doctor successor;
009
010    public String getName() {
011        return "The Doctor";
012    }
013
014    public Species getSpecies() {
015        return Species.GALLIFREYAN;
016    }
017
018    public Planet getHomePlanet() {
019        return Planet.GALLIFREY;
020    }
021
022    public int getIncarnationNumber() {
023        return incarnationNumber;
024    }
025
026    public void setIncarnationNumber(final int incarnationNumber) {
027        this.incarnationNumber = incarnationNumber;
028    }
029
030    public String getIncarnationName() {
031        return incarnationName;
032    }
033
034    public void setIncarnationName(final String incarnationName) {
035        this.incarnationName = incarnationName;
036    }
037
038    public String getSlogan() {
039        return slogan;
040    }
041
042    public void setSlogan(final String slogan) {
043        this.slogan = slogan;
044    }
045
046    public Doctor getPredecessor() {
047        return predecessor;
048    }
049
050    public void setPredecessor(final Doctor predecessor) {
051        this.predecessor = predecessor;
052    }
053
054    public Doctor getSuccessor() {
055        return successor;
056    }
057
058    public void setSuccessor(final Doctor successor) {
059        this.successor = successor;
060    }
061}
